{The girl begged in tears. “Mister, please cut off my feet...”}
]

[
{Leaving $0 on the worn cushion, #0 begins their work.},
{As if someone recently took them off, $0 are lying on the ground.},
{Moving past $0, which are neatly aligned, #0 continues with their work.}
]

[
{$0’s red enameled leather glistens in the light.},
{The ankle straps on $0 still appear elegant even though they’re worn out.},
{As if representing a long history, the heels of $0 are worn out.},
{The flawless condition the leather of $0 is in seems out of place.}
]

[
{#0 sneaks a few glances towards $0 while they’re working.},
{#0 just keeps looking over at $0.},
{Having difficulty concentrating, #0 stops working and turns around to gaze at $0.},
{Trying to resist viewing $0 again, #0 looks in the opposite direction, trying to resume the job at hand.}
